Package: fluxASCVD
Type: Package
Title: Example ASCVD Model for the flux Ecosystem
Version: 1.8.0
Authors@R: person("Jarrod", "Dalton", email = "daltonj@ccf.org", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Example atherosclerotic cardiovascular disease (ASCVD) model used to
    demonstrate the flux ecosystem. The package provides a simple,
    transparent entity-level simulation of ASCVD-related events, designed
    for instructional use and for illustrating Core, Forecast, and Validation
    workflows.
